=-----=
CLASSES
=-----=
Druid		! Spells more powerful and effective in FOREST areas.
		! Summon dryads and forest creatures in battle to help (extra dmg)

Priest		! Spells more powerful when healing.
		! Gains gold with every casting on another player (from target) 
		  (=to mana usage * modifier * level )

Nightblade	! Permanant sneak.
		! Backstab during battle. 

Battlemage	! Spells more powerful when offensive.
		- Multiple weapons.

Spellsword	! Soul trap ability/skill/spell. (Steal mana)
		! Permanant invis & sneak.
		
Paladin		! Spells more powerful when healing.
		! Destroy undead. (Implement mob types)

Master		! Permanant sneak.
		- Multiple weapons.
		! Healing spells more powerful.
		! All spells cheaper and more effective.

Thieves: 	can detect DT's
		Apply to group if groupped
